[ProMED thanks Mahmoud Orabi for this post. South Kivu (French: Sud-Kivu) is one of 26 provinces of the Democratic Republic of the Congo. It can be found on a map at https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/South_Kivu#/media/File:Democratic_Republic_of_the_Congo_(26_provinces)_-_Sud-Kivu.svg. - Mod.LL]

